OL,5,Cand ME
OL,7,FDebs Dixon caught Covid-19 at the
OL,8,Fbeginning of 2022, at a time where she
OL,9,Fdescribed herself as 'fully fit,
OL,10,Fhiking, biking, and running life at a
OL,11,Freally high level'.
OL,13,FShe experienced problems with her
OL,14,Flungs and chest infections, leading to
OL,15,Fa 'massive crash' in April.
