OL,3,CHow the Isle of Man's specialised
OL,4,Cservice is helping tackle Long Covid
OL,5,Cand ME
OL,7,FShe said: "At that point I was relying
OL,8,Fheavily on my wife. I was doing as
OL,9,Fmuch as I could possibly do at work
OL,10,Fand then coming home and doing
OL,11,Fnothing. At this point the fatigue was
OL,12,Foverwhelming."
OL,14,FBy September Debs said her body
OL,15,F'crashed completely', leading to her
OL,16,Fstaying at home for three months.
OL,18,F"It was probably the lowest I'd ever
OL,19,Fbeen in my life, I really didn't think
OL,20,FI was going to get well again.
