OL,3,CHow the Isle of Man's specialised
OL,4,Cservice is helping tackle Long Covid
OL,5,Cand ME
OL,7,FMeanwhile, representative from ME
OL,8,FSupport Isle of Man were campaigning
OL,9,Ffor a dedicated service to help those
OL,10,Fwith debilitating illnesses, such as
OL,11,FLong Covid.
OL,13,FChair of ME Support Isle of Man, Juan
OL,14,FCorlett, was one of those leading the
OL,15,Fcampaign.
OL,17,FHe said: "There was all of these Covid-
OL,18,F19 cases, which to us seemed likely to
OL,19,Fgenerate a proportion of people with
OL,20,Fpost-viral syndromes.
