OL,3,CHow the Isle of Man's specialised
OL,4,Cservice is helping tackle Long Covid
OL,5,Cand ME
OL,7,F"There was a clear link between
OL,8,Fdeveloping a virus, and developing a
OL,9,Fpost-viral syndrome and I think once
OL,10,Fwe got local politicians on board,
OL,11,Fthen the momentum built."
OL,13,FIn April 2023, .
OL,15,FSonya Chowdhury is the Chief Executive
OL,16,Ffor Action for ME, and says more
OL,17,Fservices are needed across the UK.
