OL,3,CHow the Isle of Man's specialised
OL,4,Cservice is helping tackle Long Covid
OL,5,Cand ME
OL,7,FShe said: "We sent out a freedom of
OL,8,Finformation request to fourty NHS
OL,9,FTrusts and integrated care services in
OL,10,Fthe North West, and only one came back
OL,11,Fwith a substantial service for ME.
OL,13,F"So it is quite shocking that we don't
OL,14,Fhave specific services, not least
OL,15,Fbecause of the impact of those that
OL,16,Fhave developed Long Covid and now have
OL,17,FME-like symptoms."
OL,19,FDebs concluded: "I was lucky, I was
OL,20,Fhousebound not bed-bound, there are
OL,21,Fpeople who are still bed-bound.
